{"serial": "61012", "department_serial": 56, "code": "AP3003", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Atmospheric Physics I", "ch": "大氣物理學  Ｉ"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Wang, Sheng-Hsiang"], "ch": ["王聖翔"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "S1", "room": "625"}}, {"time": {"week": 5, "session": ["2"]}, "loc": {"building": "S1", "room": "625"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 60, "department": {"ch": "大氣科學學系", "en": "Department of Atmospheric Physics"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 1, "selected": 19, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "驅動地球大氣運動與循環的能量源自於太陽輻射，而要瞭解有多少太陽輻射能量可為地球系統使用是研究大氣科學的重要課題之一。在此同時，我們必須先知道大氣成分、地表特性、雲量等影響太陽及地球輻射的因子。在本課程中，我們將分別介紹太陽輻射與地球長波輻射的特性，並了解地表與大氣的輻射平衡狀態，再以整體的探討，從加熱分布不均勻而被驅動的大氣運動，進一步討論太陽輻射與天氣與氣候系統之間的交互作用。", "en": "The source of the energy on the earth is mainly from the sun to drive the movement of air and other circulations. To understand how much solar energy can be used for earth system is a major topic of the atmospheric sciences. Therefore, it is necessary to know the components of the atmosphere, the land surface characteristics and the impact from clouds for the atmospheric radiation. In this class, we will introduce the basic theories of the radiation, the main features of the solar radiation and the planetary long wave radiation from the earth. Finally, a detailed discussion of the interaction between the atmospheric radiation and weather/climate systems will also be provided in the lecture."}, "outline": {"ch": "授課單元與大綱\n第一單元：基本原理（Properties of radiation and basic concepts）\n第二單元：輻射傳遞與平衡（Generalized atmospheric radiative transfer and equilibrium）\n第三單元：氣體吸收（Gas absorption）\n第四單元：粒子的散射與吸收（Scattering and absorption by particles）\n第五單元：輻射驅動力與氣候反應（Radiative forcing and climate response）", "en": "授課單元與大綱\n第一單元：基本原理（Properties of radiation and basic concepts）\n第二單元：輻射傳遞與平衡（Generalized atmospheric radiative transfer and equilibrium）\n第三單元：氣體吸收（Gas absorption）\n第四單元：粒子的散射與吸收（Scattering and absorption by particles）\n第五單元：輻射驅動力與氣候反應（Radiative forcing and climate response）"}, "textbook": {"ch": "1.The first course in Atmospheric Radiation (2nd), 2006: Grant W. Petty, Sundog Publishing\n2.An introduction to atmospheric radiation, 2002: K. N. Liou, Academic Poess., 583pp.\n3.An Introduction to Atmospheric Physics (2nd), 2010: David G. Andrews, Cambridge University Press", "en": "1.The first course in Atmospheric Radiation (2nd), 2006: Grant W. Petty, Sundog Publishing\n2.An introduction to atmospheric radiation, 2002: K. N. Liou, Academic Poess., 583pp.\n3.An Introduction to Atmospheric Physics (2nd), 2010: David G. Andrews, Cambridge University Press"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "20", "en": "20"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "40％   出席、作業、上課表現 (Homework assignments, student contribute to the class)\n30％   期中考試 (Mid-term exam);  30％   期末考試 (Final exam)", "en": "40％   出席、作業、上課表現 (Homework assignments, student contribute to the class)\n30％   期中考試 (Mid-term exam);  30％   期末考試 (Final exam)"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "課後", "en": "after class"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "視學生學習狀況加課2週，若沒有加課需求，加採用線上學習或自主學習", "en": "upon students' feedback"}, "domain": {"ch": "基礎學科(大氣組)\n\n\n、\n\n\n大氣遙測(大氣組)", "en": "基礎學科(大氣組)\n\n\n、\n\n\n大氣遙測(大氣組)"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "數理基礎能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "專業知識能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "資訊應用能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "國際視野與語文溝通能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "專業倫理及服務學習